      <title>德克萨斯州共和党重新选区后，民主党现任议员相互竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/26/us/politics/texas-runoff-al-green-christian-menefee.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党领导的选区重新划分努力迫使已连任 11 届的众议员艾尔·格林 (Al Green) 和国会最新议员之一克里斯蒂安·梅尼菲 (Christian Menefee) 展开争夺同一席位的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/26/us/politics/texas-runoff-al-green-christian-menefee.html</guid>
